length critical study of Warhol in print, it is also an instant classic of queer theory.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 7aART / General.2bisacsh  aAndy Warhol.  aPop Art.  aanalogical thinking.  aimitative incorporation.  aliking.  amimetic faculty.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Chicago Press Complete eBook-Package 2017z978311071193640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226505602423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780226505602.jpg  a978-3-11-071193-6  University of Chicago Press Complete eBook-Package 2017b2017  aGBV-deGruyter-alles